OL,6,FA man has been charged in connection
OL,7,Fwith a serious road traffic collision
OL,8,Fwhich left a 13-year-old boy
OL,10,FThe incident took place on Thursday 29
OL,11,FFebruary at around 6.25pm after a
OL,12,Fbrown Ford Fiesta collided with a 13-
OL,13,Fyear-old male pedestrian on Brecon
OL,14,FRoad, .
OL,16,FHarley Whiteman, 19, from Hirwaun,
OL,17,Fappeared at Cardiff Magistrates' Court
OL,18,Fon Saturday 2 March, charged with
OL,19,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,20,Fdriving and failing to provide a
OL,21,Fspecimen for analysis.
